lead_paragraph: SUN CITY, South Africa - British Open winner Henrik Stenson believes money-list rival Danny Willett will "push me to the limit" in this week's $7 million Nedbank Challenge, the penultimate event of the European Tour season.

headline.print_headline: Top Dog Stenson Expects Willett to 'Push Me to the Limit'
